OL,3,CPolice watchdog to investigate release
OL,4,Cof Manchester Airport incident footage
OL,6,FThe police watchdog is to investigate
OL,7,Fwhether someone working for the police
OL,8,Freleased footage to the media of an
OL,9,Fincident at Manchester Airport.
OL,11,FMobile phone footage appeared to show
OL,12,Fan officer kick and stamp on the head
OL,13,Fof 19-year-old Fahir Amaaz, as he and
OL,14,Fhis brother, Muhammed Amaad, 25, were
OL,15,Frestrained at the airport on 23 July.
OL,17,FFurther footage emerged days later
OL,18,Fwhich showed the lead-up to the
OL,19,Fincident.
