OL,3,CPolice watchdog to investigate release
OL,4,Cof Manchester Airport incident footage
OL,6,FIt showed two female police officers
OL,7,Fwere struck to the ground before a man
OL,8,Fwas incapacitated with a taser.
OL,10,FLast month, both brothers from
OL,11,FRochdale, appeared alongside their
OL,12,Fsolicitor Aamer Anwar at a press
OL,13,Fconference in Manchester city centre
OL,14,Fto "set the record straight... after a
OL,15,Fdeliberate attempt to smear the
OL,16,Ffamily".
OL,18,FMr Anwar spoke of the family's
OL,19,Funhappiness at the release of the new
OL,20,Ffootage and questioned how it had come
OL,21,Finto the public domain.
