OL,3,CPolice watchdog to investigate release
OL,4,Cof Manchester Airport incident footage
OL,6,FAn Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Following a press conference on 6
OL,9,FAugust 2024, when concerns were raised
OL,10,Fabout the source of a video provided
OL,11,Fto the media, we received a conduct
OL,12,Freferral from Greater Manchester
OL,13,FPolice (GMP).
OL,15,F"This referral, whilst considering
OL,16,Fother possibilities, relates to
OL,17,Fwhether someone employed by the force
OL,18,Fmay have shared footage relating to an
OL,19,Factive police investigation without a
OL,20,Flegitimate policing purpose.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
