OL,3,CPolice watchdog to investigate release
OL,4,Cof Manchester Airport incident footage
OL,6,F"We are in the early stages of an
OL,7,Findependent investigation, which will
OL,8,Fconsider whether there is any evidence
OL,9,Fto suggest this was provided by
OL,10,Fsomeone working for GMP and, if so,
OL,11,Fthe justification for this."
OL,13,FThe IOPC is also investigating the
OL,14,Factions of the officers involved in
OL,15,Fthe airport disturbance.
OL,17,FOne officer is under criminal
OL,18,Finvestigation for assault in
OL,19,Fconnection with the arrests of the
OL,20,Fbrothers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
