OL,6,FHe has also been suspended by GMP.
OL,8,FA second officer has been advised they
OL,9,Fare also under criminal investigation
OL,10,Ffor assault over an incident shortly
OL,11,Fafter two other men were arrested.
OL,13,FIn a separate investigation, GMP has
OL,14,Fpassed a "comprehensive" file of
OL,15,Fevidence to the Crown Prosecution
OL,16,FService as part of its inquiries into
OL,17,Fthe incident, which saw three of its
OL,18,Fofficers injured.
